snippet.title: Memory II - VC4000
snippet.description: This game has two modes, in the first game mode you can create your own music, or modify the short track that is included. The second game mode is a clone of Simon where you must copy the computers note, or battle against another human player. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/04/memory-ii-20-vc-4000.html
